    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">How to Use This Calculator</h2>
    <p>
      This tow truck business calculator helps you estimate the potential profitability of starting or expanding a towing operation. The calculator uses industry-standard metrics and customizable inputs to provide realistic financial projections.
    </p>
    
    <p class="font-semibold mt-4">Start by entering your basic business information:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>Company name</li>
      <li>Number of tow trucks in your fleet</li>
