      <li>Operating days per month</li>
      <li>Average tows per day</li>
      <li>Monthly growth rate</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">Financial Details</h3>
    <p>Configure your truck financing and fuel information:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Truck Purchase Price</strong> - The total cost of each tow truck, including all equipment (new flatbed tow trucks typically cost $75,000-$130,000)<sup><a href="#citation-2" id="ref-2">[2]</a></sup></li>
      <li><strong>Down Payment</strong> - Your initial payment toward each truck</li>
      <li><strong>Interest Rate</strong> - The annual interest rate on your truck loans (typically 4%-12% for commercial vehicle loans)<sup><a href="#citation-3" id="ref-3">[3]</a></sup></li>
      <li><strong>Loan Term</strong> - The length of your financing in years (usually 1-10 years, up to 25 years with SBA loans)<sup><a href="#citation-3" id="ref-3-2">[3]</a></sup></li>
      <li><strong>Fuel Costs</strong> - Average cost per gallon and miles per gallon for your trucks</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-4">
      The calculator automatically projects monthly loan payments based on your inputs. For example, a $100,000 truck with a $20,000 down payment, financed at 10% interest over 5 years, would have a monthly payment of approximately $1,700.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8">Monthly Expenses</h3>
    <p>Enter your recurring monthly expenses:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Insurance Costs</strong> - Commercial auto insurance for your tow trucks (national average is around $428 per month per truck)<sup><a href="#citation-4" id="ref-4">[4]</a></sup></li>
      <li><strong>Maintenance and Repair</strong> - Regular upkeep and unexpected repairs</li>
      <li><strong>Broker Fees</strong> - Payments to dispatch services or towing networks</li>
      <li><strong>Labor Costs</strong> - Wages for drivers and staff</li>
      <li><strong>Custom Expenses</strong> - Add any additional costs specific to your business</li>
    </ul>

